  "detailed_description": "<h1>NOTES</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Streaming / Content Creating Guidelines</h2><strong>You are welcome to stream and monetize of our game!</strong><br>Other contents creation is welcome as well.<br>Share your slapstick battle with everyone!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Phantom Theif vs Detective Slapstick online battle action!!!</strong><br>You can also have fun with someone or your friends online!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654360/extras/79074314ff81ed06f4ee86787f3591e4.poster.avif?t=1711033230\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654360/extras/79074314ff81ed06f4ee86787f3591e4.webm?t=1711033230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654360/extras/79074314ff81ed06f4ee86787f3591e4.mp4?t=1711033230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can play as a Phantom Theif or Detective, and fight with each other.<br><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Phantom Theif</h2></u><br>Blend in the crowd.<br>And, steal lots of treasures!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654360/extras/205ef777f85bb904263445ddb2aaf5f7.poster.avif?t=1711033230\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654360/extras/205ef777f85bb904263445ddb2aaf5f7.webm?t=1711033230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654360/extras/205ef777f85bb904263445ddb2aaf5f7.mp4?t=1711033230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Detective</h2></u><br>Find and arrest the Phantom Theivs!<br>Whatever it takes.<br><span 